1
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,360
"Ashes of Love"

2
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,240
"Episode 38"

3
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:52,040
Liu Ying.

4
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,180
Jin Mi, please do me a favor.

5
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,720
Now that you’ve borrowed Beast of Dreams

6
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,900
from Immortal Jin Mi,

7
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,940
just use it.

8
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:19,800
Don’t hesitate.

9
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:25,079
I’m just a little afraid of seeing the past of Mu Ci.

10
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,360
I’ll be with you.

11
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,900
Your Majesty.

12
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:56,480
Is everything fine with Sui He and Xu Feng?

13
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,620
Your Majesty,

14
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:59,120
both of them are fine.

15
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,920
They were born in the mortal world safely.

16
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:04,120
Restore Sui He’s memory immediately,

17
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:07,920
so they can cultivate feelings in this period.

18
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,020
Yes.

19
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:10,760
How about Jin Mi?

20
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:12,860
As His Majesty sent Fairy Yuan Ji

21
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,140
to guard her all day long,

22
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,579
I have no chance to kill her.

23
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:17,660
All right.

24
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,579
Try a few days later,

25
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:22,960
lest His Majesty will have something on me.

26
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,480
I see.

27
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:27,900
Is your Spirit-Vanishing Arrow ready?

28
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:29,440
Your Majesty,

29
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:32,780
as the Spirit-Vanishing Arrow
is made with my bones and blood,

30
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,020
it’ll take more time.

31
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:36,540
Please give me a few more days, Your Majesty.

32
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,780
OK.

33
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,720
I’ll give you a few more days.

34
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,800
Thank you.

35
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,740
Do you still love me?

36
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,080
Yes.

37
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,380
I’ve always loved you

38
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,520
and loved you for a long time.

39
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:25,840
However, I’ve already been in love with others.

40
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,160
As you’re neither an immortal nor a demon,

41
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,560
I can’t be with you.

42
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,520
How silly you are!

43
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:48,420
I’ve always just loved you
from the beginning to the end.

44
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:57,500
I didn’t expect that Her Majesty controlled Mu Ci.

45
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,860
She wants to hurt Jin Mi.

46
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:02,260
No.

47
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,720
We must tell Jin Mi about that

48
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:07,180
and ask her to be on guard of Her Majesty.

49
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,660
"Sweet Spring"

50
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,240
Jin Mi,

51
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,540
thanks for lending me Beast of Dreams.

52
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,780
You’re welcome.

53
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,280
If it hadn’t been for your full help
in the mortal world,

54
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,900
I would have been vanished

55
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,640
like Rou Rou.

56
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,160
I wonder whether Beast of Dreams

57
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,000
is of help to your old friend.

58
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:35,300
Jin Mi, to tell you the truth,

59
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:39,520
the one who killed Qiang Huo
with Spirit-Vanishing Arrow

60
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:41,900
that day was my old friend.

61
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,300
He is Mu Ci

62
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,900
who was kind originally.

63
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,680
He had to hurt you
as he was in others’ control.

64
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,659
If you can’t forgive him,

65
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:56,280
get even with me.

66
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:57,780
Whatever you want to do,

67
00:07:58,659 --> 00:08:00,000
I’ll bear it for him.

68
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,500
Stand up first.

69
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:23,760
Who controls your friend?

70
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,000
Her Majesty.

71
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,240
Her Majesty?

72
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,680
I don’t know why she wants to hurt you.

73
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,580
It’s better you’re in the Floral Realm now.

74
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,360
If you go back to the Heaven Realm some day,

75
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,799
be careful.

76
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,380
My Lord

77
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:46,680
the absorbing power of the
Autopsy Wild Silkworms is so strong.

78
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:48,680
In fact,

79
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:51,060
there is a way to control

80
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,340
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms

81
00:08:52,500 --> 00:08:54,000
from absorbing his magic power.

82
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,960
I raised him from his childhood,

83
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,420
so my feelings for him

84
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,540
are no less than those of Liu Ying for him.

85
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,500
I can’t bear to see him so painful either.

86
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,040
My Lord

87
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,980
I know your mind.

88
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:10,580
But the way to control
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms is...

89
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:14,560
Father

90
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:17,780
what should we do to control
the Autopsy Wild Silkworms?

91
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:29,200
Liu Ying, you’d better know nothing

92
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,400
about the way to save him.

93
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:31,640
Why?

94
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,760
Because it costs much magic power

95
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,720
of the one who saves him.

96
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:35,800
I know

97
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:36,860
you’ll sacrifice yourself

98
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,520
to save him.

99
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:40,300
However, I hate to see that.

100
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,220
Father.

101
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:44,580
No.

102
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,100
I don’t want.

103
00:09:56,180 --> 00:09:56,860
I don’t want.

104
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,180
Liu Ying,

105
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:02,100
stop.

106
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:03,160
Stop now.

107
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,240
Take your hand off.

108
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,460
I’ll save him.

109
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:07,640
I won’t live alone if he dies.

110
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,540
Silly girl, you’ll make him more painful

111
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:11,380
by forcibly transferring magic power to him.

112
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:15,740
Father,

113
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,780
what should I do to save him?

114
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:28,180
Father,

115
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,520
what are you doing?

116
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,280
Help him to get up now.

117
00:10:33,620 --> 00:10:36,840
Originally, Autopsy Wild Silkworms are unsolvable.

118
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:40,340
However, the bones and blood
of those with strong magic power

119
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:43,240
can suppress the Autopsy Wild Silkworms in his body

120
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,460
and ease his pain for a while.

121
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:51,860
However, as the one saving him
loses his bones and blood,

122
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:54,280
his magic power will decrease immediately

123
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:56,420
and he will feel very tired.

124
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:59,240
I didn’t want you to try it before,

125
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:02,720
because I feared that you couldn’t bear it.

126
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,220
Father.

127
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:09,940
I raised him since his childhood.

128
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:15,680
I know you like him sincerely

129
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:20,720
and just want you to be happy.

130
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:22,960
Father,

131
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,220
I’m sorry.

132
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,660
I know

133
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,580
when Xu Feng was grounded,

134
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:39,100
Jin Mi went to the Qiwu Palace secretly.

135
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,180
As we couldn’t kill

136
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,940
the little fairy in the mortal world,

137
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,220
the feelings between them

138
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,920
have been deeper now.

139
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,960
If you had tried hard,

140
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,400
it wouldn’t be so.

141
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,100
I’m sorry to fail you.

142
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,660
Fine. Sit down.

143
00:12:03,220 --> 00:12:04,480
Run Yu

144
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,180
always pretends to be

145
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:09,500
gentle and harmless before others.

146
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:11,180
However, no one knows

147
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,800
what he thinks.

148
00:12:13,260 --> 00:12:14,960
He showed his true self

149
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:16,540
by the Dongting Lake back then.

150
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,100
I don’t believe that

151
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,160
he doesn’t want to be Heavenly Emperor.

152
00:12:20,940 --> 00:12:22,860
Once he gets married with Jin Mi,

153
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,800
Water Immortal, Wind Immortal

154
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:25,840
and the Floral Realm

155
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:27,320
will be his power.

156
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:30,460
If Xu Feng is still

157
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:31,720
obsessed with Jin Mi,

158
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,260
there’ll be a terrible result.

159
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:39,300
All in all, Jin Mi is the biggest obstacle.

160
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:41,620
Now the only way is

161
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,840
to eliminate her.

162
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:46,300
So Xu Feng will forget her

163
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,920
and Run Yu’s support will be lost.

164
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:51,060
However, I’m afraid it is difficult to kill her

165
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:54,200
in both the Floral Realm and the Heaven Realm.

166
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:55,820
As long as I want to,

167
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,920
I can do anything in the world.

168
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,700
Mi has been to the Qiwu Palace twice.

169
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:08,040
What do you think?

170
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,600
I got her back with great efforts.

171
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,320
Originally, I want her to be carefree.

172
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:17,200
It’s fine if she likes Night Immortal

173
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,740
who is in harmony with the rest of the world,

174
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,200
so the whole family can
have a free and unfettered life.

175
00:13:23,060 --> 00:13:28,340
Unexpectedly, she falls in love with Fire Immortal.

176
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,600
I don’t care about the criticism of the Heaven Realm.

177
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:31,960
What matters is that

178
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:34,460
Her Majesty won’t be good to her.

179
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,360
Absolutely, we can’t

180
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:38,860
remain indifferent to her matter.

181
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:40,280
Her Majesty

182
00:13:40,660 --> 00:13:42,540
won’t just let us go.

183
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,200
Our quiet life

184
00:13:47,420 --> 00:13:48,800
will end.

185
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,700
I don’t care whether we can lead a free life

186
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:56,320
or have to fight against Her Majesty.

187
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,460
I just wish Mi a happy life.

188
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:00,760
However, it is really terrible as I think of

189
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,720
her experience in the mortal world.

190
00:14:03,020 --> 00:14:05,380
If she insists on staying with Fire Immortal,

191
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:07,840
I wonder Her Majesty must figure out some tricks

192
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:08,740
to hurt her.

193
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:12,120
I’m afraid it is difficult to guard against her.

194
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:13,700
I’ll find a chance

195
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,800
to make it clear to His Majesty.

196
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,540
What a wishful thinking!

197
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,960
Haven’t you seen the way he treats her

198
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,440
after Su Li’s death?

199
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:25,360
Don’t expect anything.

200
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:46,100
At first, I wanted to maker them happy.

201
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:49,620
Unexpectedly, Daddy and Auntie Lin Xiu

202
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,180
are worrying about me.

203
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,860
As his daughter,

204
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,780
I care nothing but my love.

205
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,020
Phoenix.

206
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:02,040
Now only the secret behind the veil

207
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:03,780
can make my emotions fluctuant

208
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:06,140
and make me be lost in a reverie.

209
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:08,640
How can

210
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,360
you do that?

211
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:25,560
In the mortal world, you promised to marry me.

212
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,140
Will you keep your promise?

213
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,660
I’ll explain to Daddy

214
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,280
and ask him to break off my engagement.

215
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:33,560
By that time, I’ll keep my promise.

216
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:46,960
Why is it so strange in my heart all these days?

217
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:50,740
Is everything between Phoenix
and me in the mortal world

218
00:15:51,060 --> 00:15:53,920
just impulsiveness in a flash?

219
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:57,980
It’s really like a dream to me now.

220
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:01,680
If Her Majesty really killed Rou Rou,

221
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:04,540
she will be my enemy

222
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,900
and Phoenix is my enemy’s son.

223
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:09,660
How should I face him?

224
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,380
She killed Rou Rou.

225
00:16:13,220 --> 00:16:16,380
Daddy and Auntie Lin Xiu
are worried about me.

226
00:16:16,820 --> 00:16:19,300
If I insist on staying with Phoenix,

227
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,800
I will let them down.

228
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:23,540
Daddy,

229
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,180
when did you come here?

230
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,720
You even didn’t notice that I was here.

231
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:31,160
Are you worrying about
your engagement with Night Immortal?

232
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:33,900
Marriage isn’t trivial.

233
00:16:34,340 --> 00:16:36,540
If you really destroy the
engagement with Night immortal,

234
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,700
many people will be embarrassed.

235
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:45,760
Daddy,

236
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,900
my engagement...

237
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:54,000
My engagement

238
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:56,100
will be decided by you.

239
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:59,160
I was so willful before.

240
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:02,740
I don’t know why.

241
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,180
You’re so childish

242
00:17:05,579 --> 00:17:06,800
that you always do whatever you like.

243
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,920
Do you really think it clearly now?

244
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,859
Or will you change your mind tomorrow?

245
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:13,140
I’ve made up my mind

246
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,619
and won’t change any more.

247
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:17,940
Unexpectedly, both sons of His Majesty

248
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:21,099
would be chosen by you at will.

249
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,720
The wedding date is approaching.

250
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,780
If you have made a choice,

251
00:17:25,859 --> 00:17:27,000
don’t regret it.

252
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,100
Have you really made up your mind?

253
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,760
Yes.

254
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:41,660
I won’t change any more.

255
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,300
There are complex rituals
for the wedding in Heaven Realm.

256
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:47,820
Stay with me in the Luoxiang Mansion
for a few days,

257
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,400
so Auntie Lin Xiu can teach you
the rituals in the Heaven Realm.

258
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,680
You are used to being free in the Floral Realm.

259
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,320
If you make any mistakes by then,

260
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:57,120
you’ll disgrace Night Immortal.

261
00:17:58,060 --> 00:18:00,920
I think you’re afraid that I will disgrace you.

262
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:04,760
Even so,

263
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:08,320
that’s my honor as your daddy.

264
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,060
What’s going on with Mother recently?

265
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:22,640
Her Majesty hasn’t left
the Zifangyun Palace recently.

266
00:18:22,980 --> 00:18:23,840
However, Princess Sui He

267
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,820
has often visited the Zifangyun Palace recently.

268
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,440
Continue keeping an eye on Mother.

269
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,480
By the way, Your Highness,

270
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,820
I heard that today Immortal Jin Mi
will come to the Heaven Realm

271
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:35,840
and stay in the Luoxiang Mansion
of Water Immortal.

272
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:37,100
Really?

273
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:41,080
Are you going to the Empyrean Cloud Palace?

274
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,080
Go to the Luoxiang Mansion.

275
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:44,900
His Majesty invited Xuan Ling Lord Doumu

276
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:46,420
to discuss Chan in the Empyrean Cloud Palace.

277
00:18:49,060 --> 00:18:49,900
I know.

278
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:50,860
I have a sense.

279
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:02,860
Immortal Jin Mi,

280
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:04,360
Fire Immortal is asking to see you outside.

281
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:06,780
No.

282
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,780
Tell him to go back.

283
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:11,020
Yes.

284
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:30,860
Your Highness,

285
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:32,780
Immortal Jin Mi won’t meet you.

286
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:34,200
Please go back.

287
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:36,600
What’s wrong with her?

288
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,760
Your Highness, you...

289
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:54,540
Why do you refuse to see me today?

290
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,600
Besides today,

291
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,500
Your Highness,

292
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,780
we’d better not meet each other afterwards.

293
00:20:03,540 --> 00:20:05,740
I’ll marry Night Immortal in the end.

294
00:20:06,380 --> 00:20:07,300
What?

295
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,480
When we are together,

296
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,920
my daddy,

297
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:13,400
Auntie Lin Xiu,

298
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:15,000
His Majesty,

299
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:15,980
Chief Peony

300
00:20:15,980 --> 00:20:17,360
and Night Immortal are all worried.

301
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,320
Such an worrying matter

302
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:21,060
must be wrong.

303
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,740
There is nothing wrong

304
00:20:23,140 --> 00:20:24,140
with love.

305
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,960
Jin Mi, you know my mind.

306
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:29,300
What’s more, we love each other.

307
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:30,320
Your Highness,

308
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:33,080
we once did love each other.

309
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:36,500
However, it was just the
impulsiveness of human beings.

310
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,800
As for the present,

311
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:40,260
we can’t make it

312
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:42,200
with our deep love alone.

313
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,300
I won’t allow you to marry Night Immortal.

314
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:47,400
Do you know that

315
00:20:47,620 --> 00:20:48,980
there is a witness everywhere

316
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,860
and the one destroying
others’ marriage will go to the hell?

317
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:51,840
Don’t you fear that?

318
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:52,800
I’m an immortal.

319
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,980
I’m not afraid of going to the hell.

320
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,140
I’m afraid of nothing

321
00:20:55,460 --> 00:20:57,120
in heaven and earth.

322
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:01,600
The only thing I’m afraid of

323
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,620
is your mind.

324
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,780
After experiencing hardships,

325
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,180
you were willing to accept me,

326
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:11,880
which made me really very happy.

327
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,840
In the past, I had no expectation for the future.

328
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,120
But after meeting you,

329
00:21:19,900 --> 00:21:22,100
I have been looking forward
to our future every day.

330
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,580
However, today

331
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:27,760
you even said our love was a mistake

332
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,620
and wanted to marry Night Immortal.

333
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,660
I don’t know why you change your mind suddenly.

334
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,460
Has anyone forced you

335
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:37,440
or have I done anything that made you awkward?

336
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,840
Tell me and I’ll handle it.

337
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,380
Your Highness,

338
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,520
you’re making me awkward now.

339
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:47,180
I don’t know what to do either.

340
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:50,680
Your Highness,

341
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:55,060
Lord Doumu will talk about Chan today.

342
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,400
I think you’d better go earlier for it.

343
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,400
I’ll pretend that you get
confused temporarily today.

344
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:07,160
I’ll wait for you to figure it out.

345
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:22,060
The Heaven Realm is different
from the Floral Realm,

346
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:24,020
so be careful.

347
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:28,100
Especially, don’t get close to Mother.

348
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,400
Phoenix must know something.

349
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:55,060
Your Highness.

350
00:23:04,900 --> 00:23:06,260
Keep watch on the Zifangyun Palace.

351
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:08,920
Tell me in time whatever Her Majesty does.

352
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:09,820
Yes.

353
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,000
Xu Feng.

354
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:27,400
Xu Feng,

355
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,000
as fairies in the Heaven Realm asked me,

356
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:31,180
I connected you with these Red Strings.

357
00:23:32,060 --> 00:23:35,120
I know your only love is Jin Mi.

358
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:35,880
However,

359
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:40,100
I just do so to get good luck.

360
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:42,260
You were so cruel

361
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:46,080
that you burned my innocent Red Strings.

362
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,080
Xu Feng,

363
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:53,060
you are so furious.

364
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,880
Has anyone offended you?

365
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:00,560
Uncle.

366
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:02,300
Xu Feng.

367
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:03,520
Good boy.

368
00:24:08,360 --> 00:24:10,940
Xu Feng, the discussion will begin soon.

369
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,620
Don’t stand still. Move now.

370
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,740
Let’s go.

371
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:25,000
Immortal Jin Mi.

372
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,800
Why are you here today?

373
00:24:29,100 --> 00:24:30,900
Supreme Lord Lao will distribute elixir today.

374
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:32,680
I come specially to invite Water Immortal to try it.

375
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,540
What a pity!

376
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:35,440
He has attended the discussion

377
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:37,360
of Xuan Ling Lord Doumu

378
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,420
and is not here today.

379
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,880
No one will appreciate his elixir.

380
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,740
I’m afraid Lord Lao will be disappointed.

381
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,000
Do you have time

382
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,400
to appreciate elixir in the mansion?

383
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:49,140
Me?

384
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,340
Is it appropriate for me to go there?

385
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:54,080
I can account for failing to invite your father

386
00:24:54,360 --> 00:24:56,200
as I invite you.

387
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:07,620
Leave first.

388
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,420
Yes.

389
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,160
It turns out that she is from the Zifangyun Palace.

390
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:15,040
Is it Her Majesty?

391
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:19,600
OK. Please wait for a while.

392
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,060
I’ll go in to get changed.

393
00:25:21,320 --> 00:25:23,300
I’ll wait for you here.

394
00:25:35,860 --> 00:25:36,560
Mi,

395
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,340
your practice of the Summoning Magic

396
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,740
is getting better.

397
00:25:41,120 --> 00:25:42,060
Keep your voice down.

398
00:25:48,540 --> 00:25:49,440
Mi,

399
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:50,760
are you so lonely

400
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:52,660
as you haven’t got married with

401
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,620
Night Immortal?

402
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:55,680
So you want me...

403
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,540
Stand up.

404
00:25:57,580 --> 00:25:58,740
I’m serious.

405
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:02,080
Now go to the Empyrean Cloud Palace
for my daddy

406
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:03,780
and tell him that

407
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,720
Her Majesty sends someone to take me away.

408
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:06,840
Her Majesty?

409
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,780
The Fairchild outside said

410
00:26:09,980 --> 00:26:11,720
she was a fairy of Supreme Lord Lao

411
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:13,580
and asked me to taste elixir in their mansion.

412
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:15,700
However, she is from Her Majesty’s palace.

413
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:19,020
Her Majesty is crafty and insidious.

414
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,460
You must be in danger if you go there alone.

415
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:22,480
Stay here and I’ll protect you.

416
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:23,260
It doesn’t matter.

417
00:26:23,620 --> 00:26:24,920
I must go this time.

418
00:26:25,760 --> 00:26:27,240
She killed Rou Rou.

419
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:29,000
I’ll avenge Rou Rou.

420
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,160
Ask my daddy to go there.

421
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,600
I’ll try my best

422
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:34,140
to let her admit her crime.

423
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:35,120
In this case,

424
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:37,100
we’ll gain the evidence to punish her.

425
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:39,540
OK.

426
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,460
You must be careful.

427
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,960
Immortal, please.

428
00:27:04,740 --> 00:27:05,740
Please.

429
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:31,880
This way.

430
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,100
Please.

431
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,880
"Zifangyun Palace"
Please.

432
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:49,840
As expected, it is Her Majesty.

433
00:28:55,900 --> 00:28:57,540
Fairy Jin Mi.

434
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,480
No.

435
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:02,640
I should call you Immortal Jin Mi now.

436
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:05,420
I’ve been waiting for you for a long time.

437
00:29:16,520 --> 00:29:17,320
Xu Feng,

438
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:18,980
it’s really lively today.

439
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:20,200
It seems that we’re late.

440
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:22,780
How lively it is!

441
00:29:22,860 --> 00:29:24,160
There’re so many immortals.

442
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:26,540
Xu Feng, find a seat now.

443
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,780
There is a seat.

444
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,540
I’ll take it first.

445
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:45,480
The discussion is very important today.

446
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:47,280
Why isn’t Mother here?

447
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:49,600
Your Majesty.

448
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:52,300
I was going to ask Supreme Lord Lao for elixir.

449
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:55,920
Unexpected, I was misled here
by the fairchild who didn’t know the way.

450
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,520
I’m sorry for disturbing you.

451
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,460
I’ll leave now.

452
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,960
Jin Mi was taken away
by someone of Her Majesty.

453
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:34,780
Where is Xu Feng?

454
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:44,340
It’s true that we’ll make elixir today,

455
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:48,220
but it isn’t like that of Supreme Lord Lao.

456
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:52,500
I have wondered

457
00:30:53,140 --> 00:30:57,040
what your real body is.

458
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,860
How about making elixir

459
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,780
on this lucky day?

460
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:04,520
So I’ll know more.

461
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:25,320
Your Majesty, please stop kidding.

462
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:28,420
My daddy announced to all immortals that

463
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:31,420
my real body is

464
00:31:31,560 --> 00:31:34,080
a Six-petal Frost Flower
in the Empyrean Cloud Palace that day.

465
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:37,060
Demon Zi Fen

466
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:40,300
did attract Water Immortal
with her beautiful appearance back then.

467
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:43,540
However, no one knows who your father is.

468
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:47,460
I think Even Water Immortal
can’t make sure of that.

469
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:49,360
Words are but wind.

470
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:51,920
No one has seen your real body so far.

471
00:31:52,180 --> 00:31:53,780
Seeing is believing.

472
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:56,880
Let me check

473
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:58,800
what you are actually today.

474
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,800
The hellfire can be divided into 8 levels.

475
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:25,200
I think Firefly Fire, Candle Fire and Wood Fire

476
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,000
won’t work for you.

477
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:30,560
Let’s start with the 4th level

478
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:32,980
Alcohol-brewed Fire.

479
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,360
Back then,

480
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:36,700
your mom

481
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:39,200
could stand the final level

482
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:40,780
Glazed Pure Fire.

483
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:43,700
I wonder which level you can stand.

484
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:46,500
I fully expect that.

485
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,740
That’s impossible.

486
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:50,060
My mom was Floral Immortal.

487
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,860
It was impossible for you to hurt her.

488
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:54,020
She brought disaster to herself.

489
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,660
I’m afraid you don’t

490
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,380
mean to check my real body.

491
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:33,700
I think

492
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,920
you want to kill me here.

493
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:38,260
You are quite clever.

494
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,820
When I experienced hardships
in the mortal world back then,

495
00:33:40,820 --> 00:33:42,100
you sent someone to kill me.

496
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:44,040
However, my good friend Rou Rou was killed,

497
00:33:44,100 --> 00:33:44,680
right?

498
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:45,780
So what?

499
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,860
You hurt my mom back then

500
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,900
and killed my friend now.

501
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,880
New hatred is piled on old.

502
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:54,940
I’ll get even with you today.

503
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:57,440
It’s impossible for you to do so.

504
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:36,540
I’d better tell Run Yu first.

505
00:34:48,139 --> 00:34:50,620
Your Highness, Jin Mi is in danger.

506
00:34:54,219 --> 00:34:55,760
The 7th level of hellfire

507
00:34:56,239 --> 00:34:57,420
Boiling-oil Fire.

508
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:24,380
You’re really Luo Lin’s daughter

509
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:26,820
with such excellent water control power.

510
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:28,900
Break.

511
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:42,860
The 8th level of hellfire

512
00:35:43,020 --> 00:35:44,500
Glazed Pure Fire.

513
00:35:44,580 --> 00:35:45,380
Your Majesty,

514
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:49,020
why must you kill me?

515
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:51,480
Because you’re Zi Fen’s daughter

516
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,780
with the similar appearance to her

517
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:57,200
and you even dare to seduce my son.

518
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:59,500
I must hold on and wait for my daddy.

519
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:05,800
There is no regret that
you die for thousands of times.

520
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,760
I didn’t expect that

521
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:10,140
with the supreme power,

522
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,740
you were actually afraid of me.

523
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:15,360
I’m so surprised.

524
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:16,120
I’m afraid of you?

525
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,300
I’m not afraid of you.

526
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:20,340
If you’re not afraid of me,

527
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:23,160
why do you only dare kill me with hellfire

528
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:26,560
but not face up to me directly?

529
00:36:26,560 --> 00:36:27,480
You evildoer,

530
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:30,180
I must kill you today.


